text: Graovac () is a Serbo-Croatian surname, derived from the toponym Graovo. Notable people with the surname include: *Ante Graovac (1945–2012), Croatian scientist *Daniel Graovac (born 1993), Bosnian footballer *Kristina Graovac (born 1991), Serbian handballer *Tyler Graovac (born 1993), Canadian ice hockey player ==See also== *Grahovac Category:Bosnian-language surnames Category:Croatian-language surnames Category:Serbian-language surnames
title: Graovac
